'''蒙克顿堡'''（Fort Monckton）是英国[[汉普郡|汉普郡]][[戈斯波特|戈斯波特]]的一个军事堡垒，前身是1545年建造的黑尔斯沃思城堡（Haselworth Castle），这座城堡在1556年废弃。18世纪末，英国皇家国防委员会（Royal Commission on the Defence of the United Kingdom）为了在[[美国独立战争|美国独立战争]]时期保卫[[朴茨茅斯港|朴茨茅斯港]]，在城堡遗址上建造了这座堡垒。<ref name=Kilkicker>{{cite web|url=http://www.fortgilkicker.co.uk/monckton.htm|title=Fort Monckton|publisher=fortgilkicker.co.uk|accessdate=2012-12-27|archive-date=2016-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160402195558/http://www.fortgilkicker.co.uk/monckton.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

堡垒在二战后仍由国防部管理<ref name="Williams">The Western Defences of Portsmouth Harbour 1400-1800 by G.H. Williams Portsmouth Papers No.3 Page 47</ref>，[[英国陆军|英国陆军]]称其为“一号军事训练营”（No.1 Military Training Establishment）<ref name="pastscape">{{Cite web|url=https://www.pastscape.org.uk/hob.aspx?hob_id=462038&sort=4&search=all&criteria=monckton&rational=q&recordsperpage=10|title=Pastscape - Detailed Result: FORT MONCKTON|website=www.pastscape.org.uk|access-date=2021-03-24|archive-date=2014-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006131629/http://www.pastscape.org.uk/hob.aspx?hob_id=462038&sort=4&search=all&criteria=monckton&rational=q&recordsperpage=10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[MI6|MI6]]前特工[[理查德·汤姆林森|理查德·汤姆林森]]曾说这里其实是MI6的训练中心<ref>{{cite book|title=The Big Breach: From Top Secret to Maximum Security|author=Richard Tomlinson|publisher=Mainstream Publishing|year=2001|isbn=1-903813-01-8}}</ref>。
